----
When Lord Shankar came here, when Lord Vishnu came here, they did penance here for 60 thousand years.

37
00:03:43,541 --> 00:03:45,083
60 हज़ार वर्ष
----
60 thousand years

38
00:03:45,500 --> 00:03:54,041
और अपने चक्र से वो वो चक्र्पुश्करनी बनाई, मणिकर्णिका कुंड, और भगवान् विष्णु के पसीने से वो कुंड भरा हुआ है
----
And with his Chakra he created that Chakrapushkarni, Manikarnika Kund, and that Kund is filled with the sweat of Lord Vishnu.

39
00:03:55,208 --> 00:04:03,375
