----
Which is the biggest pilgrimage site among the pilgrimage sites, then Lord Shankar named it Manikarnika Ghat.

43
00:04:35,416 --> 00:04:41,458
मणि-कर्णिका और घाट, तो चक्रपुष्करनी का नाम मणिकर्णिका में बदल गया
----
Mani-Karnika and Ghat, then the name of Chakrapushkarni changed to Manikarnika.

44
00:04:41,750 --> 00:04:45,875
तो जब भी यहाँ कोई तीर्थस्थल आता है तो सबसे बड़ा तीर्थ मणिकर्णिका है
----
So whenever any pilgrimage site comes here, the biggest pilgrimage is Manikarnika.

45
00:04:46,291 --> 00:04:52,375
interviewer: बोला जाता है कि भारत का सबसे बड़ा तीर्थस्थल मणिकर्णिका है
baba: हाँ, तीर्थों में तीर्थ
----
Interviewer: It is said that Manikarnika is the biggest pilgrimage center of India.
Baba: Yes, the pilgrimage among pilgrimages.

46
