----
Those who are very lucky people, for them there is Manikarnika, the great crematorium of Kashi.

62
00:07:06,916 --> 00:07:08,333
interviewer: ये प्रक्रिया क्या होती है
----
Interviewer: What is this process?

63
00:07:08,375 --> 00:07:14,083
baba: ये प्रक्रिया चली आ रही है सदियों से, आदिकाल के समय से
----
baba: This process has been going on for centuries, since ancient times.

64
00:07:15,083 --> 00:07:27,333
